Class FormatedStringType

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IAttributeType

    public class FormatedStringType
extends StringType
    This class is used for string that contains a formated String. Meaning that the string not only contains value, but also formating information. This makes this class e.g. not effectively searchable with parameters.
